  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your Twisted Chakra forms claws that allow you greater destructive power.</p><p>You gain the following benefits only when you are gaining the benefits of Desperate Rage or Twisted Chakra Cloak:</p><p>• You can, as a Bonus Action, make an additional 2 unarmed attacks if you spent your action making unarmed attacks.<br />• When you hit a creature two or more times in a single turn using an unarmed attack, the target creature makes a Constitution saving throw, being Dazed on a failed save until the end of your next turn.<br />• You can make opportunity attacks without spending a reaction.</p><p>You gain the following benefits while you are under the effects of Twisted Chakra Cloak:</p><p>• You can add your Dexterity modifier to one of your claw attacks once per turn.<br />• A creature triggers an opportunity attack from you for every 10 feet they move within your melee range.<br />• Your claw attacks add your Sealed Beast Level to their damage rolls.</p>",
